./reviews/dialogues/2026-05-26-whether-the-forbidden-claimant-column-does-independent-explanatory-work-.md:18:**Steelman:** The Forbidden Claimant Rubric makes a move that most comparative work skips. Instead of asking how much the practitioner contributes (the self-power and other-power axis), it asks who is permitted to own each required function. This double code, support locus plus forbidden claimant, lets the model avoid the usual reductive move of translating radical gift traditions into hidden psychological skills. If Shin Buddhism requires hearing, settled trust, and saying the nembutsu, the rubric does not call these disguised effort; it asks where each function is held and which claimant is prohibited from owning it. That preserves the tradition's own grammar while still making cross-tradition comparison possible. The rubric also generates falsifiable predictions: wrong-claimant failures should produce distinctive adverse patterns (self-power anxiety in gift practice, achievement seeking in practice-realization, reification after direct introduction). This is a real analytical contribution. If the predictions hold, the rubric would add explanatory value beyond what Pargament's coping styles, locus-of-control scales, and upaya literature already provide.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.md:31:Secondary literature gap: The audit searched Pargament, Engler, Hadot, Ferrer, Katz, Sharf, Dahl, Lutz, Davidson, Lindahl, Britton, upaya literature, Tannisho, Bendowa, and SN 45.8. It did not close-read Shinran's letters, Kyogyoshinsho, Longchenpa, Wangchuk Dorje, Christian grace manuals, Sufi fana and baqa texts, or original Pali and Japanese terms. That gap blocks any candidate-discovery claim.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.md:33:Risk of overread: High. The ledger may turn tradition-specific soteriology into analyst-owned cells. Pure Land entrusting, Dogen practice-realization, and Dzogchen recognition may not be practitioner capacities at all, even when they have observable preconditions.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.md:49:- Dogen Bendowa practice realization enlightenment are one text translation
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.md:55:- Jack Engler, Therapeutic Aims in Psychotherapy and Meditation, https://www.atpweb.org/jtparchive/trps-16-84-01-025.pdf, and Inquiring Mind interview, https://inquiringmind.com/article/0501_1_engler-interview/: overlap: Very close for prerequisite capacities, sequencing, and failure modes. Engler explicitly links meditation suitability to ego development, self-observation, affect tolerance, stability, and teacher choice of practice.; difference: Engler is mainly psychodynamic and Buddhist practice-facing. He does not supply a comparative vector ledger across grace, vow, nondual recognition, self-power, and practice-realization traditions.; novelty impact: High reduction for the capacity prerequisite claim. Remaining novelty is the multi-locus, multi-direction, cross-tradition rubric.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.md:70:Candidate: Dogen's Bendowa practice-realization, especially the claim that training and enlightenment are not two, https://www.abuddhistlibrary.com/Buddhism/C%20-%20Zen/Ancestors/Dogen/Bendowa/Bendowa.htm
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.md:72:Why it strains the model: If practice and realization are one, then load-transfer language can create the separation Dogen rejects. Zazen is not simply practitioner agency carrying a burden, nor divine or vow relocation. It is enactment of realization. The ledger can handle this only by adding values such as no-transfer, no-boundary, and analyst-frame-refused. Those values may save accuracy but weaken explanatory compression.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.md:74:Confidence effect: Lowers confidence in the model as a universal explanatory structure. It remains useful as a comparative heuristic, but the anomaly blocks promotion above novel_synthesis until Dogen, Pure Land, Dzogchen, and Christian grace cases are coded without distortion.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.md:78:- If: Capacity direction is generated by soteriology rather than only by practice technique. Then: Independent coders should infer later manual warnings and safeguards from early claims about self, liberation, and final transformation at above-chance rates. For example, Other Power texts should warn against calculation, practice-realization texts should warn against treating practice as a means to a later goal, and deconstructive paths should warn against reification and dissociation. Weakens if: Scalar maturity, broad tradition labels, or Pargament-style agency locus predict the same warnings as well as the vector ledger, or coders cannot agree on direction and locus. Test surface: Blind coding trial across SN 45.8, Tannisho, Bendowa, one Dzogchen or Mahamudra manual, one Christian grace manual, and one Sufi fana or baqa source.
