./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning-8a8d544ce3b6f17a.md:116:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.70 to about 0.55. The layered beginning structure is strongly anticipated by Rambo conversion theory, liminality, situated learning, scaffolding, Pargament agency styles, Lindbeck doctrine-as-grammar, Berger plausibility structures, Shinran Other Power, Dogen practice-realization, and prior Lumenary entry-claimant records. The remaining contribution is an extension: a split-corpus coding protocol that asks whether affordance, institutional selection, authorization grammar, and handoff density predict warnings and repair episodes without circular evidence.
